disp("*** This is a test with a number of nested scripts inclusions    ***")
disp("***                                                              ***")
disp("*** The script 'book' executes:                                  ***")
disp("*** - the instructions of the script 'prologue'                  ***")
disp("*** - some instructions                                          ***")
disp("*** - the script 'sections_of_chapter_II' which executes some    ***")
disp("***   instructions and the script 'subsections_of_section_II.2'  ***")
disp("*** - some instructions                                          ***")
disp("*** - the instructions of the script 'epilogue'                  ***")
disp("***                                                              ***")
disp("*** Here are the instructions of the script 'book':              ***")
disp("***                                                              ***")
disp("***      exec prologue                                           ***")
disp("***      . Introduction                                          ***")
disp("***      . Chapter I                                             ***")    
disp("***      . Chapter II                                            ***")
disp("***      exec sections_of_chapter_II                             ***")
disp("***      . Chapter III                                           ***")
disp("***      . Chapter IV                                            ***")
disp("***      exec epilogue                                           ***")
disp("***      The End                                                 ***")
disp("***                                                              ***")
disp("*** and those of the script 'sections_of_chapter_II':            ***")
disp("***                                                              ***")
disp("***     ... Section II.1                                         ***")
disp("***     ... Section II.2                                         ***")
disp("***         exec subsections_of_section_II.2                     ***")
disp("***     ... Section II.3                                         ***")
disp("***     ... Section II.4                                         ***")
disp("***     ... Section II.5                                         ***")
disp("***                                                              ***")
disp("*** and finaly those of 'subsections_of_section_II.2':           ***")
disp("***                                                              ***")
disp("***     ..... Subsection II.2-a                                  ***")
disp("***     ..... Subsection II.2-b                                  ***")
disp("***     ..... Subsection II.2-c                                  ***")
disp("***     ..... Subsection II.2-d                                  ***")
disp("***                                                              ***")
disp("*** The result should look like the table of contents a of book: ***")
disp("***                                                              ***")
disp("***   (this message)       < (in prologue)                       ***")
disp("***   . Introduction  < (in book)                                ***")
disp("***   . Chapter I     < (in book)                                ***")
disp("***   . Chapter II    < (in book)                                ***")
disp("***   ... Section II.1     < (in sections_of_chapter_II)         ***")
disp("***   ... Section II.2     < (in sections_of_chapter_II)         ***")
disp("***   ..... Subsection II.2-a < (in subsections_of_section_II.2) ***")
disp("***   ..... Subsection II.2-b < (in subsections_of_section_II.2) ***")
disp("***   ..... Subsection II.2-c < (in subsections_of_section_II.2) ***")
disp("***   ..... Subsection II.2-d < (in subsections_of_section_II.2) ***")
disp("***   ... Section II.3     < (in sections_of_chapter_II)         ***")
disp("***   ... Section II.4     < (in sections_of_chapter_II)         ***")
disp("***   ... Section II.5     < (in sections_of_chapter_II)         ***")
disp("***   . Chapter III   < (in book)                                ***")
disp("***   . Chapter IV    < (in book)                                ***")
disp("***   (epilogue message)   < (in epilogue)                       ***")
disp("***   The End         < (in book)                                ***")
disp("********************************************************************")
